### ──────────────────────────────────────────────
### Smart Bus System — Analytics API Integration Tests
### Uses VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### ─── 1. Login as Admin ───────────────────────
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@smartbus.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### ─── 2. Store Token ──────────────────────────
# Copy the token value from the login response above,
# then paste it below between the double quotes.
# (REST Client doesn't auto-extract JSON — manual step)
@authToken = PASTE_YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ─── 3. GET Booking Trends ──────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/bookings-trend
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ─── 4. GET Seat Preference ─────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/seat-preference
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ─── 5. POST Seed Demo (optional) ──────────
# Only uncomment if you want to re-seed from the API.
# POST {{baseUrl}}/analytics/seed-demo
# Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
# Content-Type: application/json
